rules: Rule1: If vehicle1 is deployed in region alpha, then the mission for vehicle1 is a go.
Rule2: Provided that vehicle1 is docked at platform station, it follows that vehicle1 is secured at platform station.

Rule4: Whenever vehicle1 is inspected at platform station, vehicle1 is cleared.

Rule6: Under the condition that vehicle1 is scheduled at platform station, vehicle1 is docked at platform station.
Rule7: Whenever a backup for vehicle1 is activated, the backup for vehicle1 malfunctions.

Rule8: If it is not the case that (if vehicle1 is scheduled at platform station then (if it is not the case that (if the mission for vehicle1 is not a go then vehicle1 requires refueling) then the mission of vehicle1 is aborted)), then a backup for vehicle1 is activated.
Rule9: Provided that it is not the case that (if the mission for vehicle1 is not a go then vehicle1 requires refueling), it follows that the mission of vehicle1 is not aborted.
facts: Fact1: Vehicle1 is inspected at platform station.
